These are Puzzles for 1x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-8-1::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: trance, punk
1. the fan of trance is on the right of the fan of punk##1
2. the fan of punk is not to the right of the fan of punk##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |  2  |
| Music-Genre   | punk | trance |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-8-2::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: adventure, romance
1. the person watching adventure movies is on the far right##1
2. the person watching adventure movies is not to the left of the person watching romance movies##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |
| Movie-Genre   | romance | adventure |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-8-3::.
2 different pets are kept: rabbit, snake
1. the owner of the rabbit is somewhere to the left of the owner of the snake##5
2. the owner of the snake is on the left or right of the owner of the rabbit##3
3. the owner of the rabbit is not to the right of the owner of the rabbit##8

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1     |    2     |
| Pet   | rabbit | snake |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-8-4::.
The people use 2 different means of transport: taxi, roller
1. the person driving the taxi is not to the right of the person driving the taxi##8
2. the person driving the roller is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |   2   |
| Transport   | taxi | roller |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-8-5::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: board-games, card-games
1. the person who's hobby is card-games is not to the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##8
2. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |   2    |
| Hobby   | card-games | board-games |

 #################################

 
